;; ---- the finish store phases -----------------------------------------------------
;; Eight copies of the ext leg's store phase with the h8-add prefix:
;; add the state lane, wrap to 32 bits, scatter the word back at its
;; base (the walking pointer arrived at hp+4 from the ldt-shaped
;; gather; one flatten have re-bases the walker before the guard
;; ladder). Value register 11, walker 9, byte holder 10.

